How is WEP vulnerable?
WEP protocol doesn't offer any key management which is one of the primary weaknesses.
How might you notice if someone is trying to crack WEP on a network you monitor?
Depending on the attack you might be receiving insane network traffic.
How can you protect networks from WEP vulnerabilities?
Try to mess with your keys but really just don't use WEP there's too many work arounds.
